## DISCLAIMER

This repository contains code and algorithms developed as part of a thesis project
at Chungbuk National University. While the core methodology and synthetic data generation
are open-source, the original manufacturing data used in model training is subject to
non-disclosure agreements (NDA) with the semiconductor manufacturing partner and is
NOT included in this public repository.

### Data Usage Notice:
- Sample data and synthetic datasets are provided for demonstration and reproducibility
- Original production dataset is proprietary and confidential
- Researchers wishing to collaborate on proprietary data should contact the author
- This code is compatible with equivalent manufacturing datasets following the schema defined in `src/data/schema.py`

For commercial use or integration with proprietary data, please consult with the author
or the Chungbuk National University Department of Industrial AI.

